Enum Class ExceptionEnum

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<ExceptionEnum>
it.polimi.ingsw.Utils.MessageEnums.ExceptionEnum
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<ExceptionEnum>, Constable
public enum ExceptionEnum extends Enum<ExceptionEnum>
This enumeration represents the different types of exceptions that can occur in the game.
